reviews.text: Great beef brisket but I suspect that MSG was added to their soup/food as I was so thirsty after eating. Besides, the storefront is really clean, bright, and inviting.
Always my hide away. They've great customer service and that's why there are lots of loyal customers!
The food taste is consistently good. The beef brisket and wantons are fully recommended!
good food

reviews.text: 崩沙腩好好味🤗🤗🤗
換咗老細冇以前咁好食。
牛什，牛腩，魚旦粉麵不錯，魚旦粉要一讚，好味，魚旦有鮮味！
主打潮州粉麵，但牛什河一般般，食落口啲牛什好多渣，而且連飲品仲要40幾蚊有啲貴。
牛什粉麵比較出色。
